snippet.title: Wizard101 Official Console Announcement
snippet.description:
Wizard101 + console = a magical match! 🪄

You've been asking, and now it's happening! Soon, players will be able to pick up their controllers and traverse the Spiral on Nintendo Switch, PlayStation, and Xbox consoles. 

Stay tuned for more information!
